        {
            "id": "https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/mou-xue-xiao-cun-zai-yue-quan-da-bao.html",
            "url": "https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/mou-xue-xiao-cun-zai-yue-quan-da-bao.html",
            "title": "某学校体检系统存在越权",
            "content_html": "\n<figure class=\"post__image\">经过信息收集，发现了这个web网站<br>在谷歌浏览器打开时一直弹窗请在微信客户端打开<br>经过抓包分析，开发者只是在前端调用js进行限制，于是直接修改js<br><img  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/Tu-Pian-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"559\" height=\"153\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-2-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>成功绕过限制<br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/Tu-Pian-1-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"404\" height=\"486\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-2-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-2-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-2-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-2-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-2-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-1-2-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<figure class=\"post__image\">这种登录框居然不用密码，于是我随便输入了姓名和sfz<br>发现没有网络请求就进入了<br>很奇怪的逻辑...<br><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/Tu-Pian-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"407\" height=\"511\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-3-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p> </p>\n<p>在js中一番努力的寻，发现了大量接，又是一番测，皇天不负有心人啊<br>在/api/ReportApi/GetReportDetail<br>请求方法：POST<br>请求参数：regNo<br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">响应说明：返回报告详情JSON<br></span></p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\"><br>发现每次请求的格式都是<br>{\"encryStr\":\"Bzyg2W5zHFZi8QDchXkD+NRw3oQ0h+eCabdmBl0x80wZXgQO0NNPrxbyPmobHYkeKVJv15qEZ8e0FjJm02KVEvtS7mp2plVdvZ7m8l3ctjbaLKGSlpYhzTSSn14Co92Qp+CX/sxiKj07rsdHIzBVFw7GE+JLWf0TLa+a1n3etCQ=@vhV9ngNuSLo73bPgJXI6qcA2174FUkzhmxyJeqQM1XM=\"}<br><br>于是我有又开始js逆向<br>分析出加密逻辑是<br></span>先生成临时密钥 l<br>格式是：当前秒级时间戳 + 6位随机大写字母。<br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">用 l 加密业务数据<br></span>把 payload 转成紧凑 JSON 字符串，使用 AES-ECB + PKCS7 加密，再做 Base64，得到 data_part。<br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">用固定主密钥加密 l<br></span><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">固定密钥是 abcdefgabcdefg12。<br></span>同样 AES-ECB + PKCS7 + Base64，得到 key_part。<br><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">拼接最终字符串<br></span><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">encryStr = data_part + @ + key_part<br>然后我开始猜测regno的组成<br>猜测无果，于是又转向了信息收集<br>收集到了一个教师sfz<br>默认密码sfz后六位进去后，提示更改密码，但是更改密码的接口应该是有问题，响应包显示修改成功，但还是原密码（—_—）<br>成功获取到regno的格式<br>250424001636<br>应该是日期＋序号<br>于是我开始对regno进行遍历<br><img  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/Tu-Pian-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"607\" height=\"238\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-5-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>有响应了<br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/Tu-Pian-6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"251\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-6-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>保存后看一下<br><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/Tu-Pian-7-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"509\" height=\"284\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-2-xs.png 640w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-2-sm.png 768w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-2-md.png 1024w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-2-lg.png 1366w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-2-xl.png 1600w ,https://Fuzzy-World.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/Tu-Pian-7-2-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure><br>成功越权<br><br><br><br><br></span></p>",
